<P>
   In an age when politicians seem able to ``emote'' anything, New
York City Mayor Rudy Giuliani is a gloriously feeble actor.
Assuming, that is, that Hizzoner even bothers to try _ which he
usually does not. Make a few sympathetic comments about unarmed men
killed by policemen? Not on your life, Mister. Keep financing a
museum that has annoyed you? Fugeddabahdit. A few routine
courtesies to your opponent? Whodya think you are, lady? &QL;
