 &HT;    Shopping on the Web
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service AUSTIN, Texas _ www.applianceorder.com
<TEXT>
_ Serving the Central Texas area, this local site is one of a few
reliable places on the Web to buy big home appliances. Everything
from washers and dryers to ovens are available and shipping is
free.
<P>
   MUST BUY: Frigidaire 5.0 cubic foot chest freezer, perfect for
storing cold cuts, $194 with free shipping.
</P>
<P>
   www.zanybrainy.com _ Zany Brainy, the retail chain that
specializes in nonviolent and educational toys for kids, has a
comprehensive Web site with exclusive toys as well as name brands
you can buy online.
</P>
<P>
   MUST BUY: Green Orbit school microsope set, $30 plus $4.25
shipping.
</P>
