</P>
<P>
   ANTI-SEMITIC (San Francisco) _ The number of anti-Semitic
incidents in California increased last year while the number
nationwide declined, according to an annual audit released
Wednesday by the Anti-Defamation League, or ADL. By VENISE WAGNER.
</P>
