   _A scarf joint will be almost invisible when attaching two
lengths of chair-rail or baseboard molding (comes with
illustration).
</P>
<P>
   _How to fix a crooked door.
</P>
<P>
   _Peeling paint can have numerous causes. Here's a couple of
possible solutions.
</P>
<P>
   _Horizontal copper wires installed on roof shingles to deter
moss growth will NOT attract lightning strikes.
</P>
<P>
