SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; SECRET-ASPAR &LR;  _ Few preparations of asparagus are
as delicious as Zibibbo's Asparagus and Leek Escabeche. This is
only one of the many tapas-style dishes that has become the
hallmark of this Mediterranean restaurant in Palo Alto.
<P>
   This is the latest installment of the regular column describing
what makes a Bay Area restaurant's dish a success, we'll tell how
to make it.
