<HEADER>
A4659 &Cx1f; tab-z
u v BC-ECOMMERCE-ADVISORY-NY     04-12 1134
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ECOMMERCE-ADVISORY-NYTSF </SLUG>
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   (am/th)
</P>
<P>
   THIS ADVISORY WAS TRANSMITTED WEDNESDAY, April 12.
</P>
