   &UR; EDITORS: These articles are from The New York Times' E-Commerce
special section of March 29. This is the final weekly installment
of three 12- to 14-article packages. To publish any of these
``separate-buy'' feature articles, they must be purchased from one
of the following New York Times Syndicate sales representatives: &LR;
