   FBN-DRAFT-VOLS_ Tennessee safety Deon Grant of Augusta, Ga., was
the nation's top defensive back last season. But some scouts are
concerned about Grant's ability to cover and tackle. Still, he
should go in the top 15 picks (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 14.
