<P>
   BC-NY-CANCER-MAPPING-NYT (moved on Tuesday, April 11)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Tuesday, April 11,
about the New York State Health department's publication of breast
cancer data misstated the department's Web address. The site is
www.health.state.ny.us/nysdoh/cancer/csii/nyscsii.html
</P>
<P>
   BC-SCI-ANTIOXIDANTS-NYT (moved on Monday, April 10)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Monday, April 10,
about new recommended levels of antioxidants like Vitamin C and E
misstated the given name of a pediatric nutritionist who is a
spokesman for the American Dietitic Association. He is Dr. Keith
Ayoob, not Kenneth Ayoob.
</P>
